headline: Fidelity buys $60M in Bitcoin, files first Solana ETF application with CBOE
summary: Fidelity Investments made waves by purchasing $60 million in Bitcoin through its FBTC ETF while filing the first-ever spot Solana ETF application with the CBOE.
